Text: A large number of damaged sentries have been detected in this area. Their memory chips must be recovered to determine the cause of their demise.
However, the gargantuas in the area make recovery difficult.
Outside assistance is required if this operation is to succeed. Please recover the chips and bring them to me.
Analysis of the data has concluded that this destruction was wrought by one of our own!
Insufficient memory chips to complete analysis...the mission has been deemed a failure. Further recovery is impossible─retreating.
Halt, tax evaders! On behalf of the Wing of Protection, we hereby place you under arrest!
All that stock... You peddlers must be rakin' it in.
S-Somebody help! These bandits won't leave us alone!
I thought this would be easy money...
Thanks for driving those bandits away!
The parcels are safe, and so are we!
Time to gather up our inventory and head back to town.
Forget the merchandise, let's get out of here!
I hope those peddlers were carryin' somethin' to eat!
Listen, we're just playin' the hand we were dealt. Don't go judgin' us.
\\<bleep> ErRoR! Revising forecast... Expect wildfire conditions, not wintry woe!
\\<bloop> eRrOr! Revising forecast... Expect blizzard conditions, not violent zephyrs!
\\<bleep> erRoR! Revising forecast... Expect hyperelectricity, not searing sunshine!
\\<bloop> ErROr! Revising forecast... Expect gale-force winds, not shocking storms!
Target detected just ahead. Please eliminate it with extreme prejudice.
Destruction of the rogue unit confirmed. Thank you for your assistance.
Lost sight of target. Mission failed...
Rogue unit must be dealt with. Requesting assistance...
Irregular behavior detected from organisms within this district.
The target has fled. Our mission ends in failure.
This body isn't made for combat, so I'll hang back.
Analysis complete. Rogue unit detected. Please eliminate it on sight.
The jungle itself was laid waste...
He's watering the seeds with aether...

Look out!
They're much bigger now!
Watch where the roots are facing!

Smash them!
Whatever face they wear!
They don't seem interested in us...
After a rival predator, it seems.
Everything is food to this creature...
It must take the qualities of its prey!

Big ones, little ones...
The whole family is here!
What kind of bird can do that!?
The shards are resonating with its magic!

Did you see that?
The spell came from the crystals!
We'll face whatever he throws at us!

Well enough...
Let's get back to it!
Time to go on the offensive!
Well, that's one way to fight.
Was that a blade just now?
They mean to drop bombs on us?

His strength is formidable...
But so is ours!
Once we determine a pattern, we can avoid its attacks.
We have more to be wary of now...
Dodge its attacks, then resume the offensive!
Get caught in that, and you're done for...
Do they <Italic>1</Italic>really<Italic>0</Italic> need so many weapons?
All we have to do is dodge. Easy...right?
What manner of weapon is this?
Careful! It makes ready to strike!
I'd rather not get shocked if I can help it.
The air is thick with lightning aether.
Careful not to touch those barriers.
I shudder to imagine being covered in that.
Welcome to Yesterland! The long wait is finally over!
For the parade of mascots is soon to begin! Join us in our revelry─you won't regret it!
Round and round we go. Won't you join us?
A moment of death is the only rest from this eternal march!
The parade goes on and on. On and on!
Show us just how bright the life within you can shine!
Now, let the parade of the fantastic begin! Join if you dare!
There's only so much I can accomplish on my own...
Many thanks! This is more than enough!
Without materials, my repairs will have to wait...
Those moles left the ruins manyholed and tunnelfilled!
Mobbie senses goodly earthgifts on the surface ripe for the taking!
What a disappointment... No soundsleeps for Mobbie tonight...
Hah hah hah, splendid! March on, my friends, march on!
Oh my, it appears that while the spirit is willing, the body is weak. It seems our parade must come to an end... Perhaps the next one will be more lively!
Although today's parade may be over, rest assured we will return...
They better not come this way...
I'll take whatever materials you find!
Can you feel it? The festive spirit is thick in the air, and our revelers call out for a deathly display!
Now is the time to look back upon your eternal memories, and be dazzled by the light of life! Be dazzled, before pounding feet snuff it out!
The parade shall continue forevermore! All are welcome!
In a life eternal, we grant a moment of death! Savor it!
Life itself marches to the beat of the parade!
Thank you, one and all, for joining our parade!
I'm afraid to say that our march must come to an end. However, we will return─of that you can be certain!
I suppose Mica did not deign to appear...
Thank you, one and all, for joining in our parade!
I'm afraid the festivities must come to an end. But we will meet again soon─of that you have my word!
I wonder if Mica is ready...?
The clearing is full of nastyshrooms!
They mean to dirtymake our precious craftclay!
Too many mushrooms! Bagnobrok will leave fightyhurts to the outlander!
The mushrooms are no more! Bagnobrok is filled with joysmiles!
But an oddscent hangs in the air. From the mushrooms, perhaps?
A huge, hulking angrybeast! Best for Bagnobrok to run away.
The mushrooms are still sporestrong... What will become of the craftclay?
Time to go and gather helphands! Be safe, outlander!
Does he ever run out of mammets!?
What in the hells are you doing!?
C-Call them off! Call them off, dammit!
My festive Endless, welcome to the final stretch of our macabre march!
By popular demand, we have invited a very special guest! Brace yourselves for a fantastic show!
Give a hearty round of applause for Mica the Magical Mu!
Let your flickering life shine bright, one last time!
I hope you enjoyed the show! And with that grand finale, our march must come to an end!
Thank you, one and all, for taking part! Although your legs may be tired, do take care on your way home!
That one! That's the real Ellerete!
We must retreat before it's too late...
And that marks the end of our parade! I hope you enjoyed Mica's grand display!
Very rarely are we offered a taste of death. I only hope you drank deep while you could!
And if you feel unsatisfied, rest assured we shall meet again. For this parade is eternal!
Not good─we need to spread out!
D-d-don't you think we've come far enough?
N-n-n-no! It's just... It's just... Did you hear something?
Not this again! I told you there's no such thing as─
Here they come! Are you ready?
Not that I'm scared or anything.
I'd say it's time for a tactical retreat...
I'd say that was mission accomplished, then!
We contractors have to stick together, eh?

Threat assessment: high.
Bypassing safety protocols.
It's not a question of if, but when.
Then how will we hold the tower? There's only two of us!
Thanks to you, the tower still stands.
At least until the next swarm comes.
Dammit! There are too many of them!
We can't stay here any longer!
Dammit! I'm almost out of souls!
I'll be back as soon as I can. Good luck.
I'm back! Now where are the blood-sucking bastards!
Oh... Well, I hope you don't think I was just waiting for you to finish now... Heh heh.
I...uh, suppose then I should be heading back. Thanks again, traveler!
That was the last of my soul reserves...
Another day, another commission of paramount importance...
I'll pump you full of lead!
Time for you to bite the bullet!
Run? Seemed to work well for you last time.
Everyone? It is now, unless you have a pair of Lalafells in your pack.
And just what are we supposed to do if that <Italic>1</Italic>thing<Italic>0</Italic> shows?
Barely! What do you think the elders will do when they see us empty-handed?
We could always try and find someone to join us...
And let them take all the glory?
Tell me again how much glory we've accumulated so far?
Is that what I think it is?
Do you think it's a giant weasel? Then yes. It's <Italic>1</Italic>exactly<Italic>0</Italic> what you think it is.
I knew this was a bad idea...
Too many of them, and far too few of us.
The blade of Kirlirger is unrivaled!
I'm no match for Kaqool Ja!
Don't know how many are left out there. You'd best get to safety, too, while you can.
Our current strength is insufficient. We require reinforcements...
The extermination was a success thanks to external support.
All units, cease combat maneuvers and return to base.
We have failed to contain the organism.
We must withdraw and form a new strategy!
I told you. Didn't I tell you?
Mission accomplished. Thank you for your assistance.
We did it! We actually did it!
The elders aren't going to believe this.
They'll believe it when they eat it! Start carving!
I think what they <Italic>1</Italic>mean<Italic>0</Italic> to say is, thank you, traveler. For everything.
Do you remember when I said this was a bad idea?
I'm going to need a bigger axe... And a sharper one... And maybe another one...
What say next time we stick to nutkins?
Ow... Has anyone seen my finger?
How long's it been since we gave someone a proper beating? Two...three bells?

Stand still, now!
Heh heh heh!
The boss is going to hear about this!
Thought a round of fisticuffs'd leave me with a sense of fulfillment. Yet why do I feel so empty?
Not enough stabbing, I reckon. Might be we should do some more.
I don't got to do nothin'!
<Italic>1</Italic>I'm<Italic>0</Italic> not the one who let himself get striped by this here streak of birdshite.
But...I can't have your failings besmirch me sparkling reputation now. Let me show you lot how it's done.
Yeah! Show us how it's done!
And that, my boys, is how one does a proper stabbin'.
Scanning for signs of the rogue unit...
Let's deal with the ones in the way!
My pack is near bursting, but I suppose I could find room for a <Italic>1</Italic>few<Italic>0</Italic> more fronds...
This dill will save the lives of many. We are all in your debt!
Now, to remove this core and─ Uh...
You sure you say you're not a hunter?
'Cause I reckon they could use a bastard as mean as you.
I'll see you around then? Thanks again for the help!
We must return to safety at once.
Please, you have to do something!
I can't die here... Not like this!
Allow me to learn from your example.

Ah, your positioning
is spot on.
For this exercise, I cannot assist you...
No...I must hold out a little longer!
Time to show off my brushstrokes!
Right! Let's sweep this deck clean!
He lay in wait for us...
Do they usually grow that large...?
Such monstrous lungs that creature had...
I thought punutiy were meant to be timid...
I'll never look at a punutiy the same way again!
Whatever it is, the path leads onwards!
We'll have to find another route.
This fellow seems quite at home...
We can't simply sneak by...can we?
We can't simply sneak by...can we?
Out of the tunnels we go!

Careful now.
This fiend's a vicious one.
It's the vilekin we saw earlier.
My axe for a giant boot!

The Skyruin falls today!
For Tuliyollal!
The wind... It's all around us!
Heh... This will be some fight.
This is not a safe spot to stand...

Hmph...
A beast is a beast.

Ugh...
I need to pay more attention!

The sky, the ground...
It's all changed!
But they won't be far behind...
